info.name: TRON Legacy-style tumblr logo
info.description: Replaces boring tumblr logo font with a TRON Legacy font. With a TRON Light Cycle thrown in just for kicks.

style.css: @namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml); @-moz-document url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com/'), url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com/')   { #logo {height: 0 !important; width: 0 !important; padding-left: 350px !important; padding-top: 44px !important; background: url(http://media.tumblr.com/d2168ec24f0761c63a0dd5025edc453d/tumblr_nf0l1bt1HF1rgoq1io1_250.png) no-repeat !important;}}
